data.description: Welcome to this charming vintage home nestled in a prime location near Legacy Park, Carl Miller Park, and St. Luke's Hospital. Built in 1959, this beloved residence exudes character and warmth, offering 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and 2,352 square feet of timeless living space. As you approach, you'll be greeted by its inviting curb appeal, including a large driveway that adds convenience and charm to the property. Step inside to discover a cozy interior featuring a beautiful fireplace with a rock splash, creating a nostalgic ambiance perfect for gatherings with loved ones. With its spacious layout and desirable location, this home provides the ideal setting for creating cherished memories. Don't miss the opportunity – schedule a showing today!
